name: К
description: To be honest, even now I do not fully understand what NFT is, and what will happen with it in 5 years is a mystery to me. In my opinion, it is impossible to predict the development of technology. Everything is changing very rapidly. But the only thing I know for sure - no matter where technological progress takes us, the ability to think and feel, to translate your experience into lyrics, music or paintings can only a person, only an artist.
